init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The power of Mana is returning.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens, however, are not going to let that happen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are afraid that the people will use it to rise up and destroy them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens decide to take drastic measures to prevent this from happening.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens attack the Mana tree in an attempt to destroy it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The only way to destroy it is to destroy the shield.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They decide to send a spy into the human world to find out how they can destroy the shield.
